title: Yu☆Gi☆Oh! 5D's
sinopse: In an alternate version of Yu☆Gi☆Oh 5D's, Yuusei and his friend, Sect, are dueling in Satellite when a Skeleton Knight from an urban legend appears, forcing Yuusei to duel him for Sect's freedom. In Neo-Domino, Rex Godwin is planning a tournament known as the D1 Grand Prix while Jack heads into Satellite and confronts Yuusei, who in this version, he seems to not know...
